## Phase 9: Security Audit & Mainnet Deploy  
**⏱️ 2–3 days | 🟢 Antigravity**

### Step 9.1 — Automated Audit

```bash
# Submit to Sec3 X-ray (free automated audit)
# Go to: https://pro.sec3.dev
# Upload your Anchor program
# Review findings and fix critical/high issues
```

### Step 9.2 — Manual Review Checklist

- [ ] All PDA seeds are deterministic and collision-free
- [ ] Owner-only instructions verify `ctx.accounts.owner == identity.owner`
- [ ] Oracle-only instructions verify oracle authority
- [ ] No integer overflow in reputation/payment calculations
- [ ] Emergency pause works on treasury operations
- [ ] Soul-bound NFTs cannot be transferred
- [ ] Daily spending limit resets correctly
- [ ] Multisig threshold enforced for large payments

### Step 9.3 — Deploy to Mainnet

```bash
# Switch to mainnet
solana config set --url mainnet-beta

# Fund deployer wallet (need real SOL)
# Deploy
anchor deploy --provider.cluster mainnet-beta

# Note the new Program ID → Update all configs
```

### Step 9.4 — Update Frontend for Mainnet

Ask Antigravity:
```
Add a network switcher to the app:
- Support devnet and mainnet-beta
- Store in localStorage
- Update ConnectionProvider endpoint accordingly
- Show network badge in Navbar (green for mainnet, amber for devnet)
- Update all Explorer links to use the correct cluster
```

